profile_positions.description:
• Full legal support of DTEK GRIDS business (7 operational companies - DSOs and 2 service companies);
• Managing of Land and Property Function;
• Managing of transformational  and new assets integration projects;
• Supervisory Board member of 7 Ukrainian DSOs; 
• Member of Risk Management Committee;
• Member of Purchasing Committee;
• Member of HSE Committee;
• Compliance Officer;
• ESG report and strategy development group member;
• Leader of the powerful team numbering more than 160 employees in 9 companies.

Functional duties:
•	Proceeding documents drafting;
•	Representation of clients’ interests before court regarding civil, business, criminal, administrative, labor disputes; representation before state officials;
•	Legal counseling;
•	Paper flow, inquiry records and lawsuits arrangement.
